      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Sensitivity of hemolysis predictions to blood viscosity and power-law exponent variability is acknowledged but formal uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2. Nominal material properties from ISO 10628 were used."
    },
