      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "The FDA critical path study used a single well-characterized pump specimen. Sample-to-sample variability assessment is not required at MRL 2 for this credibility factor."
